text: National Highway 701A, commonly referred to as NH 701A, is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 1. NH-701A runs in the state of Jammu and Kashmir in India. == Route == NH701A connects Baramulla and Gulmarg in the state of Jammu and Kashmir. == Junctions == : Terminal near Baramulla. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 701A on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Jammu and Kashmir Category:Transport in Baramulla
